"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Liquidity\\n\\nAn enum indicating the liquidity role of the fill. Possible string values are:\\n\\n- `TAKER` – The order removed liquidity from the order book (matched an existing order).\\n- `MAKER` – The order added liquidity to the order book (rested before being matched).\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/types/liquidity#liquidity\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>An enum indicating the liquidity role of the fill. Possible string values are:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><code>TAKER</code> – The order removed liquidity from the order book (matched an existing order).</li>\\n<li><code>MAKER</code> – The order added liquidity to the order book (rested before being matched).</li>\\n</ul>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/types/liquidity.mdx#liquidity\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nAn enum indicating the liquidity role of the fill. Possible string values are:\\n\\nTAKER – The order removed liquidity from the order book (matched an existing order).\\nMAKER – The order added liquidity to the order book (rested before being matched).\\n\",\"title\":\"Liquidity\",\"titles\":[]}]}}"
